The Duck Avenger with Spike the bee in The Secret Origin of the Duck Avenger. The Duck Avenger's first appearance in an American comic was a 3-part story titled The Secret Origin of the Duck Avenger, where Ludwig Von Drake has Donald becoming the Duck Avenger and has him working alongside Spike the Bee against the Evronians.
